data.description: Indulge in the epitome of luxury living with this stunning custom-built residence nestled in the prestigious Park Haven Community of Lawrenceville, GA. Boasting three sides of exquisite brickwork, this meticulously maintained home is a true masterpiece. Sprawling across 3,800 sq. ft. of Gross Living Area, the residence encompasses five full bedrooms, five full baths, and a well-appointed half bath. Step into a world of elegance, where every detail has been carefully curated to create a haven of comfort and style. Recent upgrades elevate the interior, featuring new hardwood flooring on the stairs, plush newer carpet throughout, and bamboo flooring in two bedrooms. The Kitchen is a Chef's Dream, with a newer expandable island, dual stoves, and customizations that include dimmable lighting. Entertain effortlessly in the Family room adorned with tasteful bookcases and upgraded lighting fixtures. A state-of-the-art alarm and intercom system add an extra layer of security and convenience. The rear of the home reveals a newer shed with electrical amenities, a screened-in covered porch for relaxed evenings, and a professionally landscaped yard with illuminating lights and a sprinkler system. What sets this Home apart is its unique location, backing directly up to the sprawling 711-acre Tribble Mill Park. Nature enthusiasts will revel in the proximity to two serene lakes, walking/hiking trails, pavilions, and horseback riding trails. Imagine having this outdoor paradise as an extension of your own backyard! The full list of updates and highlights will be available upon Showing. Photos capture the essence, but experiencing this immaculately maintained home in person is a journey into unparalleled luxury. Don't miss the chance to call this extraordinary property "Home" - a true masterpiece awaits your personal touch!
